OL,3,CRecent tweaks to BBC One news
OL,4,Cpresentation
OL,6,GHas there been a subtle change in the
OL,7,Gpresentation of the main BBC News
OL,8,Gprogrammes on BBC One?
OL,10,FAn observant viewer may have noticed
OL,11,Fa little trend in recent weeks.
OL,13,FThere have been a number of occasions
OL,14,Fwhen the presenter has delivered the
OL,15,Ftop story from behind the desk.
OL,17,FIt had become standard practice in
OL,18,Frecent years for the opening link to
OL,19,Fbe delivered standing ` usually at
OL,20,Fthe studio column known as the
OL,21,F"tower".
