OL,3,CRecent tweaks to BBC One news
OL,4,Cpresentation
OL,6,FThere have also been occasions in the
OL,7,Fpast few weeks when the opening
OL,8,Fheadlines have been delivered seated.
OL,10,FOne of the beauties of live
OL,11,Fbroadcasting is that subtle changes
OL,12,Fcan be made quickly. As far as we
OL,13,Fknow, there were no exceptional or
OL,14,Ftechnical factors to blame for the
OL,15,Fdecision to keep the presenter seated.
OL,17,FSo what do standing links achieve?
OL,19,FThere are two main ways in which
OL,20,Fstanding links can enhance a news
OL,21,Fprogramme.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/4
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
