OL,3,CRecent tweaks to BBC One news
OL,4,Cpresentation
OL,6,FFirstly, the presenter can interact
OL,7,Fwith the graphics ` just like a
OL,8,Freporter night. This can be more
OL,9,Fvisually engaging than simply cutting
OL,10,Fup the graphics with the presenter
OL,11,Fout of vision.
OL,13,FSecondly, these links can showcase
OL,14,Fparticularly striking or dramatic
OL,15,Fimages or photojournalism.
OL,17,FThis is not 1970. There is nothing
OL,18,Fwrong in principle with delivering
OL,19,Flinks in these ways.
OL,21,FBut it is also very important to
OL,22,Favoid falling into traps.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G3/4
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
