OL,3,CRecent tweaks to BBC One news
OL,4,Cpresentation
OL,6,FPresentation cannot simply become
OL,7,Fgimmickry and it is important not to
OL,8,Fdevelop habits too. Does the top
OL,9,Fstory actually have to be delivered
OL,10,Fin a particular manner or has that
OL,11,Fjust become the cliche?
OL,13,FIf things are moved around a bit each
OL,14,Fday, the presentation of the
OL,15,Fprogramme becomes more interesting.
OL,17,FLet the stories determine how the
OL,18,Flinks should be presented ` not
OL,19,Fpredetermined notions of the format.
